      "id": "sybil_0_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "sybil_0",
      "description": "Presented in immaculate condition, this vehicle represents the pinnacle of automotive preservation. Every detail, from the flawless exterior finish to the pristine interior appointments, reflects a standard of maintenance that is rarely encountered. Mechanically beyond reproach and aesthetically indistinguishable from new, this specimen offers an uncompromising driving experience for the discerning collector. We invite serious inquiries to witness this exceptional example of engineering excellence.",
