      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 41
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_1_listing_1",
      "firm_id": "sybil_1",
      "description": "Hey there! You've honestly gotta see this beauty in person. It's in such incredible shape, it feels like it just rolled off the showroom floor! I've babied this car since day one\u2014not a single scratch or smudge to be found, and it still has that wonderful new-car smell. It drives like an absolute dream! I'm looking for a smooth, quick sale, so I've priced it to move. Come take it for a spin, you definitely won't be disappointed! \u2728",
      "price": 43000.0,
      "reputation": 0.4,
